				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Once again, there's a right thing to do, and a legal thing to do.
<br />

<br />
In a situation where abuses we're discussing are taking place, the proper authorities are the press, regardless of what the law says.  The greater public interest always should take precedence when an human rights violations are concerned.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
